  "description": "The first lesson: restraint. Minimal supersaw spread at 0.2, sub sine for warmth, no shimmer at all. Pure clean signal with a breath of chorus for stereo width. The Guru says: before you reach for the sky, learn to stand on the ground. Compelling at C3 vel 80 with macros zeroed.",
